                    <p class="detail-info text-success" style="font-size:1.3rem;display:none;">The picture will be shown for 30 sec and then 5min will be given to write a story on it.Candidates will also have to write number of character,their age,sex and mood.The instruction will be explained before the test.The story has to be  written about the situation in the picture,what led to that situation and what should be the outcome of the situation.After writing the story candidates will be given 1 minute turn by turn to narate their stories (the sheets on which the candidates wrote story would be taken away so one must remember what story they wrote at the time of narration.)Once narration is over candidates will have to discuss on it and are expected to arrive at one common story.</p>
